metadata.name: CyberKongJR #1
metadata.description: CyberKongJR is the genesis project for Don's NFT, building the first NFT Comic marketplace and publishing house!! A collective of independent artist and creatives in web3 harmony. Don's NFT: Buy, Trade, and Sell digital comics living on the blockchain. CyberKongJR is a character from Synth City Tales turned into a NFT Derivative. It is a derivative of all that is NFT. Think NFT pop culture meets Hanna-Barbera meets Ninja Turtle action figure. Look for a Solana knockoff soon. This project is not associated with other projects but merely pays homage to those that came before with a fun take on NFT colloquialisms and society.
